## Labels — `<%= @project.full_path %>`

Manage labels for this project. All requests require a personal access token passed in the `PRIVATE-TOKEN` header.

**Base URL:** <%= Gitlab.config.gitlab.url %>/api/v4/projects/<%= @project.id %>

**Authentication:**

```bash
curl <%= Gitlab.config.gitlab.url %>/api/v4/projects/<%= @project.id %>/labels \
  -H "PRIVATE-TOKEN: YOUR_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN"
```

---

### List Labels

```bash
curl "<%= Gitlab.config.gitlab.url %>/api/v4/projects/<%= @project.id %>/labels" \
  -H "PRIVATE-TOKEN: YOUR_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN"
```

**Query parameters:**

- `search` (optional) — Search term matched against label title
- `page` (optional) — Page number (default: `1`)
- `per_page` (optional) — Items per page, max `100` (default: `20`)

**Pagination headers returned:**

| Header | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `X-Total` | Total number of labels |
| `X-Total-Pages` | Total number of pages |
| `X-Page` | Current page |
| `X-Per-Page` | Items per page |
| `X-Next-Page` | Next page number (empty if on last page) |
| `X-Prev-Page` | Previous page number (empty if on first page) |

---

### Get a Single Label

```bash
curl "<%= Gitlab.config.gitlab.url %>/api/v4/projects/<%= @project.id %>/labels/:id" \
  -H "PRIVATE-TOKEN: YOUR_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN"
```

- `:id` — Label ID

---

### Create a Label

```bash
curl -X POST "<%= Gitlab.config.gitlab.url %>/api/v4/projects/<%= @project.id %>/labels" \
  -H "PRIVATE-TOKEN: YOUR_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"title": "bug", "color": "#e11d48"}'
```

**Fields:**

- `title` (required) — Label name
- `color` (required) — Hex color code (e.g. `#e11d48`)
- `description` (optional) — Label description
- `rank` (optional) — Sort order; lower values appear first

---

### Update a Label

```bash
curl -X PUT "<%= Gitlab.config.gitlab.url %>/api/v4/projects/<%= @project.id %>/labels/:id" \
  -H "PRIVATE-TOKEN: YOUR_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"title": "bug", "color": "#dc2626"}'
```

**Fields:**

- `title` (optional) — New label name
- `color` (optional) — New hex color code
- `description` (optional) — New description
- `rank` (optional) — New sort order

---

### Delete a Label

```bash
curl -X DELETE "<%= Gitlab.config.gitlab.url %>/api/v4/projects/<%= @project.id %>/labels/:id" \
  -H "PRIVATE-TOKEN: YOUR_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN"
```

Returns `204 No Content` on success.
